Iran will not let U.S. President-elect Donald Trump rip up the nuclear deal it signed with world powers, President Hassan Rouhani said on Tuesday.&#8221; wants to do many things, but none of his actions would affect us &#8230; Do you think the United States can rip up the JCPOA (the Joint Comprehensive Plan of Action nuclear deal)? Do you think we and our nation will let him do that?&#8221; Rouhani said in a speech at University of Tehran broadcast live on state television.-Reuters